THANK YOU ALL for your love and support. We were swamped yesterday but ended the day with a profound sense of gratitude. Thank you for the orders and for your patience, especially with any delayed pickups/deliveries. We feel so overwhelmed by this initiative to support black owned businesses and the Black Lives Matter movement at large. We hope to continue this momentum in the fight for justice and equality. .

Follow @mvmnt4blklives to stay involved and take part in the week of action in Defense of Black Lives organized by the Black Lives Matter Movement. We stand together.
